exceptions.exn: Cannot coerce IndexedUnion to an evaluable reference.

original: apply Extensionality_Ensembles. split. - intros x H. unfold IndexedUnion, FamilyUnion. apply Im_def in H. destruct H as [a H']. apply indexed_union_intro with (a:=a). apply H'. - intros x H. unfold IndexedUnion, FamilyUnion in H. apply Im_inv in H. destruct H as [a [H1 H2]]. apply H1.
